query:
INSERT INTO labelAssociations (productId, labelCode, batch, expiryDate, unitsPerPackage, packagesRead, totalUnits, associatedBy, sessionId)
SELECT 
  pwi.productId,
  '83420722D08LA129' as labelCode,
  pwi.batch,
  pwi.expiryDate,
  1 as unitsPerPackage,
  1 as packagesRead,
  1 as totalUnits,
  1 as associatedBy,
  1 as sessionId
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
WHERE pwi.waveId = 3 AND pwi.productSku = '834207'
LIMIT 1;
